athlete /ˈæθliːt/

(athletes) 

1. N-COUNT An athlete is a person who does any kind of physical sports, exercise, or games, especially in competitions. 运动员 

例： Mark Spitz was a great athlete. 马克·斯皮茨是一名伟大的运动员。 

2. N-COUNT You can refer to someone who is fit and athletic as an athlete . 运动型人 

例： I was no athlete. 我完全不是运动型的人。

